---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
	title="Shipping and Assembly Instruction PDF | PlayerStall"
	description="PlayerStall locker shipping and assembly instructions: flat-pack packaging, IKEA-style assembly, 25–30 min per locker. Print or save as PDF."
>
	<main class="pdf-installation-page">
		<div class="pdf-installation-page-inner">
			<div class="spotlight-inner-centered">
				<a href="/shop" class="spotlight-position">Shop</a>
				<h1 class="spotlight-name">Shipping and Assembly Instructions</h1>
				<div class="spotlight-meta">
					Flat-pack packaging · IKEA-style assembly · 25–30 min per locker
				</div>

				<p class="spotlight-bio">
					Our lockers are shipped <strong>individually packed</strong> in most cases—each unit arrives in its own sturdy, flat-pack box, similar to premium flat-pack furniture. This keeps every locker protected in transit and makes handling and assembly straightforward.
				</p>
				<p class="spotlight-bio">
					Each box contains all panels, hardware, and a <strong>full set of step-by-step instructions</strong> in an easy-to-follow, IKEA-style format. Plan for <strong>approximately 25–30 minutes</strong> to assemble each locker once the box is opened. No special tools are required beyond what we include or you typically have on hand.
				</p>

				<h2 class="section-title">Typical box dimensions</h2>
				<p class="spotlight-bio">
					Exact package size depends on the locker model and configuration. Below are two representative examples of how our lockers ship flat-packed.
				</p>

				<div class="installation-boxes">
					<div class="installation-box-card">
						<figure class="installation-figure">
							<img src="/images/locker-packaging-flatpack-1.png" alt="Flat-packed locker packaging – stacked panels, dimensions 75.59&quot; × 23.62&quot; × 4.25&quot;" loading="lazy" />
						</figure>
						<p class="installation-box-caption">Representative flat-pack (smaller footprint)</p>
						<ul class="installation-dims">
							<li><strong>Length:</strong> 75.59&quot;</li>
							<li><strong>Width:</strong> 23.62&quot;</li>
							<li><strong>Height:</strong> 4.25&quot;</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="installation-box-card">
						<figure class="installation-figure">
							<img src="/images/locker-packaging-flatpack-2.png" alt="Flat-packed locker in shipping box – dimensions 81.87&quot; × 27.62&quot; × 6.98&quot;" loading="lazy" />
						</figure>
						<p class="installation-box-caption">Representative flat-pack (larger footprint)</p>
						<ul class="installation-dims">
							<li><strong>Length:</strong> 81.87&quot;</li>
							<li><strong>Width:</strong> 27.62&quot;</li>
							<li><strong>Height:</strong> 6.98&quot;</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>

				<h5 class="spotlight-bio-title">Included with each locker</h5>
				<p class="spotlight-bio">
					Flat-packed components in one box, full IKEA-style assembly instructions, and hardware. Assembly time: about 25–30 minutes per locker.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="pdf-installation-footer">
				<strong>PLAYERSTALL</strong> · sales@playerstall.com · 1 888 584 1444<br>
				© 2026 PlayerStall. All rights reserved.
			</div>
		</div>

		<section class="product-main-section pdf-cta-section">
			<div class="product-container">
				<p class="pdf-cta">
					<span class="pdf-hint">Use your browser's <strong>Print</strong> → <strong>Save as PDF</strong> to download this as Shipping and Assembly Instruction PDF.</span>
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</BaseLayout>

<style is:global>
	@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oswald:wght@600;700&family=Yantramanav:wght@400;500;600&display=swap');

	.pdf-installation-page {
		font-family: 'Yantramanav', sans-serif;
		background: #ffffff;
		color: #0d0d0d;
	}

	.pdf-installation-page-inner {
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 8.5in;
		min-height: 11in;
		padding: 100px 60px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		background: #ffffff;
	}

	.spotlight-inner-centered {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.spotlight-position {
		font-family: 'Yantramanav', sans-serif;
		font-size: 13px;
		letter-spacing: 4px;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: #8c8c8c;
		text-decoration: none;
		display: inline-block;
		margin-bottom: 10px;
	}

	.spotlight-position:hover {
		color: #fe5900;
	}

	.spotlight-name {
		font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
		font-size: 42px;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: #0d0d0d;
		margin: 10px 0 15px;
	}

	.spotlight-meta {
		font-family: 'Yantramanav', sans-serif;
		font-size: 14px;
		color: #8c8c8c;
		margin-bottom: 25px;
	}

	.spotlight-bio-title {
		font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
		font-size: 16px;
		font-weight: 600;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		margin-bottom: 10px;
		margin-top: 40px;
	}

	.spotlight-bio {
		font-family: 'Yantramanav', sans-serif;
		font-size: 15px;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: #666666;
		margin-bottom: 30px;
	}

	.section-title {
		font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
		font-size: 18px;
		font-weight: 600;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		margin-top: 50px;
		margin-bottom: 25px;
		color: #0d0d0d;
		letter-spacing: 2px;
	}

	.installation-boxes {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 40px;
		margin: 30px 0;
	}

	.installation-box-card {
		background: #f7f7f7;
		border: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
		border-radius: 4px;
		padding: 20px;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.installation-figure {
		margin: 0 0 15px;
		overflow: hidden;
		border-radius: 4px;
		background: #ffffff;
	}

	.installation-figure img {
		width: 100%;
		height: auto;
		display: block;
		vertical-align: top;
	}

	.installation-box-caption {
		font-family: 'Yantramanav', sans-serif;
		font-size: 14px;
		color: #8c8c8c;
		margin: 0 0 15px;
	}

	.installation-dims {
		font-family: 'Yantramanav', sans-serif;
		font-size: 15px;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: #666666;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding-left: 0;
		list-style: none;
		display: inline-block;
		text-align: left;
	}

	.installation-dims li {
		margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
	}

	.pdf-installation-footer {
		margin-top: 60px;
		padding-top: 30px;
		border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 12px;
		color: #8c8c8c;
		max-width: 900px;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
	}

	.pdf-installation-footer strong {
		color: #0d0d0d;
	}

	.pdf-cta-section .product-container {
		max-width: 1300px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 20px;
	}

	.pdf-cta {
		text-align: center;
		margin-top: 24px;
		padding: 24px;
		border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
	}

	.pdf-hint {
		font-family: 'Yantramanav', sans-serif;
		font-size: 14px;
		color: #666;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.pdf-installation-page-inner {
			padding: 60px 20px;
		}
		.spotlight-name {
			font-size: 32px;
		}
		.installation-boxes {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}

	@media print {
		.top-bar, header.header, nav, footer, .pdf-cta-section { display: none !important; }
		.pdf-installation-page-inner {
			padding: 0.5in;
			max-width: none;
		}
		body { background: #fff; }
	}

	@page { size: letter; margin: 0.75in; }
</style>
